---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Thank You | Smart Termite Tulsa"
  description="Your termite inspection request has been received. Here's what happens next."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Thank you — we received your request.</h1>
      <p class="sub">A team member will follow up within one business day with next steps. While you wait, here's what to expect.</p>

      <h2 style="margin-top:32px;">What happens next</h2>
      <ol style="line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>We review your request</strong> and match you with the right local termite professional based on your area and what you're seeing.</li>
        <li><strong>You'll get a follow-up call, text, or email</strong> (whichever you preferred) within one business day to confirm details and schedule.</li>
        <li><strong>The inspection itself</strong> typically takes 45 to 90 minutes on-site. The inspector walks you through what they found before leaving.</li>
        <li><strong>You receive a written summary</strong> within 24 to 48 hours, including recommended next steps — no pressure to act immediately.</li>
      </ol>

      <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:30px;">
        <a href="/tulsa-termite-warning-signs" class="btn btn-secondary">Read the Warning Signs Guide</a>
        <a href="/termite-warning-signs-checklist" class="btn btn-secondary">Get the Printable Checklist</a>
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Back to Home</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
